list.name: Default Changelist
list.comment: tiles.pl: removed unused predicates and added dummy_reference/0 to reference dynamic predicates generated by data_predicate_dynamics/1 and not used in tiles.pl. dom.pl and listut2.pl: added dummy_reference/0 to references predicates not (yet) used. Fixed node_compile.js to use ng.proscriptls_path. node_goal_module.js: added proscriptls_path. decode_instruction.js: fixed to use parseInt around predicate key strings. dom.js: extended proscriptls_init to call unusedPredicates; changed clear_directives handling to happen last and to only 'empty' system, not initializations to improve predicate reference analysis. dump.js: extended danglingPredicates to check module_exports; added unusedPredicates function. bootstrap_js.pl: added at_end_of_stream/0, peek_code/1, and writeq/1 to exports; changed findall/3 to use findall/4. debugger.pl: added $traceR/3 to exports; commented out $trace predicates (not used). wam_compiler.pl: added save_compiled_state/1, consult_atom/1, repl/1, call_atom/2; removed unused predicates.

task.summary: Default task

Metapredicate definition for predicate_dom_create_object.
Updated version_date.txt.
Documentation for modules. Improved compilation documentation.
Minor doc fix.
Fixed bench Makefile to use wam_bootstrap_master.pl.
rebuilt demo state.
Updated the 'about' documentation.
Updated version to 1.0.0.
Fixed elseif directive to be elif.

Changed data_predicates.pl to a module. Changed data_predicates/3 definitions in tiles.pl to list argument of data_predicate_dynamics/1. Changed data_predicate_dynamics/1 to assert data_predicates/3 facts with current module prefix on 2nd arg (predicate). Moved consult_atom/1 to wam_compiler from boostrap_js. Changed proscriptls_init function to 'clear' directives after they have been processed. Extended generate_system_goal and predicate_generate_initialization_goal with Module param. Fixed transform_body/6 for once(X) to handle case where var(X). Added process_delayed_initializations/0 call to consult_atom/1 and consult/1.
Changed web_test_utility to display unit test progress bar and info.
Updated version to 1.1.0.

Fixed handling of nested meta-predicates across modules.
Fixed data_predicates.pl: declared meta-predicates assert_data/2, assert_id_datas/1, assert_datas/2, and assert_datas/1; fixed assert_data/2, assert_id_datas/1, and assert_datas/2 to handle nested modules; extended several predicates to expect module in parameters. Fixed foreign.js: extended predicate_define_dynamic_predicate to allow 'Module : (Name/Arity)' input format; extended predicate_retract_clause to handle 'Module : Head' input. Fixed read.js is_punctuation_charAt typo - was using object.chartAt, should have been object.charAt. Fixed bootstrap_js.pl: added dynamic/1 meta_predicate and extended dynamic/1, save_clausea/1, retract/1, and retractall/1 to handle (Module : X) input terms. Fixed wam_compiler.pl: fixed define_dynamic_predicate1/1 to pass Module info through to define_dyname_predicate/1 instead of concatenating Module and Functor; extended compile_clause_2/1 and compile_head/8 to handle (Module : X) terms, changed compile_body_arg/11 clause for MetaArgType = (:) with guard (\+ var(Arg), \+ functor(Arg, (:), 2)) to have guard (var(Arg); \+ functor_is_qualified(Arg)) - this now converts most Term to (Module : Term); added compile_body_arg/1 clause for (Module:Head :- Body); fixed compile_body_arg/1 for (Head :- Body) to use (\+ functor_is_qualified(Head)) instead of (HeadFunctor \= (:)); fixed transform_meta_expression/3 to handle (Module : Term) input param; extended save_clause/1 to handle (Module : Term) input param. Extended dump.js to support running the browser as well as the console (i.e. command-line node.js). Changed define_dynamic_predicate/1 to expect (Module: Term) instead of just (Term).
Updated version to 1.2.0. Minor documentation fixes.

Fix to compile explicit ':'. Added data_predicates:labelled_values/3.
The ':' fix was to the clause of wam_compiler:compile_body_arg/11 that handles the general arg-as-structure case with MetaArgType of 0..9 or '^'. This fix supports 'call(Module : Goal)'. The labelled_values/3 predicate returns a key/value list of values defined for the specified data prefix and ID: labelled_values(Module:Prefix, ID, Values).
Updated version to 1.2.1.

Extended doc with builtin-pred framework.
Created generate_predicate_doc.pl module to generate predicate documentation from src/docs/predicate_doc.pl. Moved write_list/(2,3) and capitalize/2 to new system_util.pl module - make them available to swipl and browser/node environments.
Completed doc for DOM builtins.

Removed ProscriptLS interpreter area from tiles.html.
Generated engine and state files.

Added numbervars/3 and canonicalized goal_function conversion.
Changed version to 1.2.1+ . Added numbervars/3. Refactored to create copy_term function. Fixed goal_function case in convert_method_argument function to use numbervars and copy_term to canonicalize the 'goal' for creating functions. This allows multiple goal_function conversions of terms that only differ in variable naming to use the same function, which in turn allows removeEventListener to match event functions. Fixed read.js/format_term function to handle numbervars option for TAG_STR case correctly. Fixed debugger.pl to use_module(system_util) to access capitalize/2 predicate.
Changed get_object_container to throw exception when object does not exist.
Update version to 1.2.2.

Added doc for several standard predicates. Added 'runtime' cat.
Documented: compare/3, atom/1, integer/1, float/1, compound/1, ground/1, = /2, == /2, functor/3, arg/3, =.. /2, copy_term/2, halt/0, current_prolog_flag/2, set_prolog_flag/2, and repeat/0.

Made debugging changes to look at stack. Added cut to reduce choicepoints.
gc.js: Added gcWrite function and gc_environment global var. wam.js: Added commented-out code to invoke dump_environments and dump_choicepoints functions when stack is large. wam_compiler.pl: Added cut to compile_head_arg/7 predicate penultimate clause to reduce needless choicepoints on stack.
Fixed comment.
Updated generated files for comment change.

Created wam_index_predicates.pl.
This module extends predicate compiled clauses with indexing.

Made generated indexing instructions relocatable using labels.
Fixed index_sequence to be a flat list.

Fixed indexing. Added new instructions to assemble.
decode_instructions.js: added switch_on_term, switch_on_constant, switch_on_structure, try, retry, trust, and goto_clause. wam_assemble.pl: Fixed encode_opcodes_1 try_me_else clause to use aux_address_of instead of address_of; added retry_me_else, switch_on_term, switch_on_constant,and switch_on_structure to encode_opcodes_1/6; added encode_label_or_fail/5, encode_switch_table/5, encode_switch_table_targets/4, and encode_switch_table_target/4 predicates; added encode_opcode/3 clauses for switch_on_term, switch_on_constant, switch_on_structure, try, retry, trust, and goto_clause. wam_index_predicates.pl: extended wam_index_clauses1/2 to assemble the indexing abstract instruction terms to concrete instruction words; fixed handling of lists; removed unused 'Base' parameters; and removed dead switch_instruction1/3 code.

Added bootstrap utility to add index clause. Implemented index instructions.
wam.js: implemented switch_on_term, switch_on_constant, switch_on_structure, try, retry, trust, and goto_clause; added gotoAddress and search_table functions. wam_index_predicates.pl: extended wam_index_clauses1/2 (was wam_index_clauses1/1) to edit base clauses for sequences and to add the index clause. wam_bootstrap.pl: extended dump_predicate/1 to record the key of the index clause. wam_bootstrap_util.pl: added add_index_clause_to_predicate/1 and edit_clauses_for_index_sequences/2.

Fixed indexing to handle atoms, integers, and floats.
wam.js: changed switch_on_term to take atom, integer, and float tables separately instead of as a single constants table. Fixed indexing instructions to handle failure (using 'if(!backtrack()) {return wamExit(false);}' cliche); fixed switch_on_constant and switch_on_structure to use 'VAL(argument)' instead of 'argument'; fixed try to set 'L' (changed retry and trust to use 'L'); fixed search_table to set search limit to tableStartPosition+tableSize. wam_assemble.pl: Fixed encode_opcodes_1/6 switch_on_term clause to expect atom, integer, and float arguments. wam_compiler.pl: added wam_index_predicates module; extended compile_file/1 to support 'index(Mode)' arg to enable/disable indexing; changed compile_stream/1 to invoke wam_index_predicates/0. wam_index_predicates.pl: fixed use_module directives to be conditional for wam_bootstrap, wam_bootstrap_util, url, and system_util; added '$indexing_mode'/1; added mark_predicates_indexed/0; changed wam_index_predicates/0 to be conditional on '$indexing_mode'(basics);refactored wam_index_predicate/1 to create compiled_clauses/2; changed wam_index_clauses/2 to use register_indexed_predicate/1; changed clause_sequence/5 and index_sequences/3 to use new head_*_in_first_arg/1 predicates; fixed index_sequences/3 to set control instruction to nop2 on singleton sequence; removed counter args from several predicates; changed index_sequence/9 and analyze/6 (was analyze/4) to determine atom, integer, and float sequences instead of just 'constant' sequence. wam_bootstrap.pl and wam_bootstrap_util.pl: added indexed_predicate/1.

Extended indexing to compiled compiler.
foreign.js: changed to use compilation_environment (this can be used to support tracing compiler); extended lookup_atom/2 and extended lookup_functor/3 to allow 'index' to be ground and other arg(s) to be var; added integer_list_to_term_array and integer_list_list_to_term_array functions; extended dump_tables/1 to dump indexed_predicates array; added indexable_compiled_predicates/1; fixed add_clause_to_predicate/3 to only set is_public to true for non-dynamic predicates; and extended type_error to give context. wam.js: added indexed_predicates global; fixed gotoAddress to use clause_keys; and added compile_buffer_codes/1. wam_index_predicates.pl: changed to use indexing_mode/1, lookup_functor/3, and compile_buffer_codes/1. wam_bootstrap.pl: changed dump_tables/1 to dump indexed_predicates, added reserve_predicate for compile_buffer_codes/1, indexing_mode/1, set_indexing_mode/1, indexable_compiled_predicates/1, register_indexed_predicate/1, compiled_clauses/2, add_index_clause_to_predicate/1, and edit_clauses_for_index_sequences/2. wam_bootstrap_util.pl: added compile_buffer_codes/1, set_indexing_mode/1, and indexing_mode/1, extended lookup_functor/3 to allow Functor/Arity to be nonground and N to be ground; similar for lookup_atom/2 and lookup_float/2; and fixed edit_clauses_for_index_sequence/2 to use nop2.

Fixed indexing to run bench programs
crypt.pl: added c/1 for debugging. wam.js: Fixed switch_on_term to use FAIL_ADDRESS constant (= 1000000) instead of 0; fixed switch_on_term for TAG_REF to use offset of 0 (using clause's control instruction) instead of offset 2 (skipping the control instruction); fixed search_table to use limit of (tableSize*2)+tableStartPosition. wam_assemble.pl: fixed to generate new FAIL_ADDRESS. wam_index_predicates.pl: moved mark_predicates_indexed/0 to wam_bootstrap_util.pl. wam_bootstrap_util.pl added set_indexing_mode/1 export.

Added hash and binary search tables for switch instructions.
Fixed FAIL_ADDRESS to be 1000000 (was mistyped as 100000 in someplaces). Extended wam_index_clauses1/2 to skip 'degenerate' sequences (a sequence of sequences is degenerate if all of the sequences are singletons). Changed test/3 to be dynamic in web_test_utility.pl to allow for the use of clause/2 on it (since dynamic and public are currently the same flag in ProscriptLS).

Fixed switch_on_structure instruction, extended benchmark.
Fixed wam.js switch_on_structure instruction to call search_table_type function correctly. Fixed search_table_type throw to reference 'type' instead of undefined 'T'. Fixed wam_assemble.pl encode_opcodes_1/6 for switch_on_structure to use encode_switch_table_typed/8. Added tak and boyer tests to 'all' for bench/Makefile: fixed tak.pl to use cut - test now works; with new indexing feature the boyer.pl benchmark test now works.

Enabled indexing for doc gen and tiles example.
Changed node_compile.js to set indexing mode to basic. Changed docs Makefile to compile type_reference.pl with indexing.

Extended to indexing the compilation of wam_compiler. Fixed wam bugs.
Extended switch_on_term to switch on different constant types: atom, integer, and float. decode_instruction.js: Changed switch_on_constant and switch_on_structure to have a hash/sequence indicator argument and to decode the address args and tables of the switch instructions. wam.js: Fixed handling of state.num_of_args to set it whenever state.current_predicate is set. (This fixes a bug in having ProscriptLS compile wam_compiler.pl.) wam_bootstrap_util.pl: Fixed indexable_compiled_predicates/1 to check (and exclude) dynamic predicates.
Extended indexing to tests.

Extended compilation of proscriptls_state.js to index system.pl.
Fixed system modules to explicitly use supporting modules: debugger.pl, promise.pl, and url.pl use bootstrap_js.pl. Removed reverse/2,3 from debugger.pl to use version in bootstrap_js.
Extended bench compilation to index common.pl and hook.pl.

Changed indexing mode to default to 'basic'.
Removed explicit setting of indexing mode to basic from compilations in Makefiles. Changed default compilation_environment.indexing_mode to 'basic' from 'none'. Changed predicate_indexing_mode to default to 'basic' when compilation_environment.indexing_mode is undefined. Changed wam_index_predicates/0 to using indexing if '\+ indexing_mode(none)'.
Disabled index compilation messages.
Fixed comment
Added benchmark data and reporting. Fixed crypt.pl.
Updated some generated files.
Updated some generated files.

Added dangling reference analysis. Fixed dangling references.
Created danglingPredicates function in dump.js. Extended preprocess/3 to write an initial line '/* This file generated automatically. It defines the runtime engine for ProscriptLS.*/'. This allows sloccount to skip generated files.

Improved use of danglingPredicates. Added singleton var reporting.
The dynamic predicates defined by data_predicates are not defined until the data_predicates initialization is called. Calling this initialization before running danglingPredicates avoids bogus dangling warnings. Created board_position_top_left_coordinates/4 in tiles.pl to resolve a dangling warning. Changed Makefile dist/proscriptls.js and examples/Makefile proscriptls_state_tiles.js targets to always run danglingPredicates. Moved dump.js from tools to engine. Added node_dangling_references.js to dist. Fixed read_term/3 in read.js to not list var starting with '_' as a singleton. Fixed singleton variables in bootstrap_js.pl, debugger.pl, not.pl, and type_references.pl. Added danglingPredicates to node_exports_init.js.

Reorganized node_*.js, created node_tools dir.
Removed unused get_count/1 from hook.pl. Fixed singletons in reducer.pl and tests.pl. Moved node_compile.js to node_tools. Deleted node_dangling_references.js. Created node_goal_module.js refactored from node_goal.js. Changed proscriptls_for_compile.js to proscriptls_engine_for_node.js. Added danglingPredicates call to proscriptls_init function. Changed dumpWrite to check for console.log or print functions. Moved copy_term/2 into analyze_singletons/4 (was /3).
Fixed doc for compilation. Refined singleton to allow '_'+lower.
